In [6]:
# report_ser (or statistics_df or audit_df) contains the theoretic moments
mean, cv = twelve_dice.report_ser[('agg', 'ex1')], twelve_dice.report_ser[('agg', 'cv')]
sd = mean * cv
import scipy.stats as ss
fz = ss.norm(loc=mean, scale=sd)
